<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:black">When you book ambulance system will ask you which emergency service you need. In a medical emergency you should ask some question including: </span></span></span></p>

